<View height="100%" controllerName="UI5FioriForTools.controller.MainNavigation.Primary.Example4" 
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns="sap.m">
    <Page class="sapUiContentPadding" title="List Report Floorplan (List)">
        <content>
            <List id="list" updateFinished="onUpdateFinished" items="{path:'/Employees'}">
                <headerToolbar>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <Title id="title" />
                    </Toolbar>
                </headerToolbar>
                <items>
                    <StandardListItem title="{FirstName} {LastName}" iconDensityAware="false" iconInset="false" type="Navigation" press="onPress"/>
                </items>
            </List>
        </content>
    </Page>
</View>